EN: I like to lay a soft blanket on the couch.

ZH: 这条毯子几年来一直保持着原样。
EN: This blanket has remained the same for several years.

ZH: 他在睡觉的时候总是抱着他的毯子。
EN: He always sleeps with his blanket.

